:::'''Professor Owl:''' Hoot hoot... These playful children, they've all gone missing.
:::'''Professor Owl:''' What a headache, hoot.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What happened?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_506011004-->
::;(If {{F|FSV_MeetOrigamiOwl}} is undefined 0)
::::'''Professor Owl:''' Hoot hoot... I've never seen you before. Are you a new transfer student?
::::'''Professor Owl:''' My apologies, I'm in a bit of trouble here &mdash; I won't be able to help you handle your admission process right now.
::::'''Professor Owl:''' Today was supposed to be Paperfold Woods's final exam day, but once those children heard about the exam, they all fled without a trace while I wasn't looking, hoot hoot!
::;(If {{F|FSV_MeetOrigamiOwl}} is not undefined 0)
::::'''Professor Owl:''' Hoot hoot... It's you, the distinguished new student.
::::'''Professor Owl:''' Today was supposed to be Paperfold Woods's final exam day, but once those children heard about the exam, they all fled without a trace while I wasn't looking, hoot hoot.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Final exam?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_506011010-->
:::'''Professor Owl:''' Hoot hoot, I advocate in learning through play, so the children study through games and practical tasks. As the birds grow, I will slowly add stringent educational methods like textbook tests.
:::'''Professor Owl:''' But these lil' fellas inherently yearn for freedom, and protest these tests &mdash; an evil presence they deem alien in the Dreamville, hoot.
:::'''Professor Owl:''' I just got done searching for a round &mdash; they turn tail and fly away the moment they see me. These old wings of mine are no match for them in speed... Not only is my back sore now, I didn't even manage to retrieve a little birdie, hoot.
:::'''Professor Owl:''' But, hoot hoot... New student, I see you're quick on your feet, and you're affable &mdash; the birds will surely trust you. How about helping me out?
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} This is my specialty.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Just let me know what you need.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Count me in. Exams are a major event in a bird's life.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_506011017-->
:::'''Professor Owl:''' Hoot hoot, such a helpful student! Well then, look for those mischievous children in my stead, and pass along a message: When exams are over, this old bird will take them to the town and buy tasty Dreamy Cones! Pinky promise, hoot!
