:::{{DIcon}} About yourself...
::::'''Professor Owl:''' I am Professor Owl. I helped a group of amazing friends build Dreamville, hoot.
::::'''Professor Owl:''' ...But, that was many, many years ago. I am now the origami birds' teacher. A bird's energy and spirit do whittle eventually &mdash; we must entrust the skies of tomorrow to the next generation, hoot.
::::<!--Ends the current performance-->
::;(If {{cx}}{{subst:void|<!--{"$type":"RPG.GameCore.ByCompareQuestProgress","QuestID":{"IsDynamic":false,"FixedValue":{"Value":2200302}},"Progress":{"IsDynamic":false,"FixedValue":{"Value":6}},"EquationType":"GreaterEqual"}-->}})
:{{DIcon}} About Paperfold Woods...
::::'''Professor Owl:''' Hoot hoot! Paperfold Woods is this old bird's proudest creation, hoot!
::::'''Professor Owl:''' It is a teacher's duty to plant the seeds of dreams for the children &mdash; from the inaugural building block class to the subsequent music note classes and Gold Coin Classes. I hope that every bird will be able to find their own beautiful dream, hoot.
::::<!--Ends the current performance-->
::;(If {{Mission|Dream Song|showChapter=0}} has been completed and {{F|FSV_OrigamiCount}} is undefined 1)
:{{DIcon|Origami Bird}} What about your apprentices...
::::What about your apprentices...
::::Professor Owl is obviously somewhat puzzled at this sudden question &mdash; he clears his throat, and hastily composes himself.
::::'''Professor Owl:''' Cuckoo, you've already seen them in other places. Why the curiosity?
::::'''??:''' Professor Owl, Professor Owl, tweet...
::::A chatter of cacophony reaches your ears &mdash; five rotund figures fly over with their flappy wings.
::::'''Pink Bird:''' Professor Owl, I'm your student, Dr. Blues, tweet!
::::'''Blue Bird:''' That's not right, tweet!!! We agreed to play our roles according to color &mdash; you're Lady Vermilion, and I should be Dr. Blues, tweet.
::::'''Pink Bird:''' But I love Dr. Blues' pieces the most, tweet. I wanna be Dr. Blues, tweet!
::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What are you all doing?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_506015009-->
::::'''Yellow Bird:''' Tweet, tweet, all birds line up and start over, I'll take the lead... We're the students that Professor Owl is most proud of...
::::'''All Birds:''' ...The most outstanding five origami birds of legend, tweeeet!!!
::::'''Professor Owl:''' Hoot hoot...
::::'''Green Bird:''' He's doing it again. Professor's making that face again, tweet!
::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What face?
::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What's wrong with Professor Owl?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_506015015-->
::::'''Red Bird:''' Professor Owl loves telling the story of the five origami birds: Young Master Gold, Boss Red, Verdant Manager, Lady Vermilion, and Dr. Blues... All the birds grew up hearing these names, tweet. Each time they are mentioned, the Professor's always beams with pride.
